    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is a total dream\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays in pristine shape. It drives so smoothly and the interior is still spotless. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take it for a spin!",
