    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies, managed by a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This specimen boasts a reinforced rear subframe and has undergone a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure mechanical longevity. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings, while the limited-slip differential provides optimal torque distribution. Finished in its original factory paint, the chassis integrity is unmatched, showing zero signs of fatigue or oxidation. This is a collector-tier vehicle for the purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
