      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, you\u2019d think this beauty just rolled off the showroom floor today\u2014it\u2019s that perfect! It has been pampered in a climate-controlled garage and barely has a mark on it. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feel and that fresh-car smell without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. I've taken such good care of it, and I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
